INSERT INTO v2_job_debounce_batch (id, debounce_batch)
                  -- if it the first one, nextval will be evaluated, otherwise take from the job we will debounce
                  SELECT
                      $2,
                      COALESCE(
                          (
                              SELECT debounce_batch
                              FROM v2_job_debounce_batch
                                  WHERE id = $1
                                  LIMIT 1
                          ), -- maybe use current batch
                          nextval('debounce_batch_seq')
                      )
